'''Vnas''' was a location at [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. The [[Battle of Vnas]] was fought there in [[1 BBY/Legends|1 BBY]]. During this battle, the [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|BTL Y-wing starfighters]] proved their value against the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]].

==Behind the scenes==
Vnas has never been exactly identified. The Battle of Vnas was only described as the "Battle of Vnas at Duro". Vnas is not another planet in the [[Duro system/Legends|Duro system]] and Duro has no moon thus Vnas was probably one of the [[City-ship/Legends|space city]] [[Orbit/Legends|orbiting]] Duro.

